name: reset
description: Reset server to minimal default: remove channels, roles (except @everyone), emojis, stickers.

description_localizations.bg: Нулира сървъра до минимални настройки: премахва канали, роли (без @everyone), емоджита и стикери.
description_localizations.cs: Obnoví server do minimálního stavu: odstraní kanály, role (kromě @everyone), emotikony a nálepky.
description_localizations.da: Nulstiller serveren til minimum: fjerner kanaler, roller (undtagen @everyone), emojis og klistermærker.
description_localizations.de: Setzt den Server auf den Minimalzustand zurück: entfernt Kanäle, Rollen (außer @everyone), Emojis und Sticker.
description_localizations.el: Επαναφέρει τον διακομιστή σε ελάχιστη κατάσταση: αφαιρεί κανάλια, ρόλους (εκτός @everyone), emoji και αυτοκόλλητα.
description_localizations.en-GB: Reset server to minimal default: remove channels, roles (except @everyone), emojis, stickers.
description_localizations.en-US: Reset server to minimal default: remove channels, roles (except @everyone), emojis, stickers.
description_localizations.es-419: Restablece el servidor a su estado mínimo: elimina canales, roles (excepto @everyone), emojis y stickers.
description_localizations.es-ES: Restablece el servidor a su estado mínimo: elimina canales, roles (excepto @everyone), emojis y stickers.
description_localizations.fi: Palauttaa palvelimen minimitilaan: poistaa kanavat, roolit (@everyone säilyy), emojit ja tarrat.
description_localizations.fr: Réinitialise le serveur à l’état minimal : supprime les salons, rôles (sauf @everyone), émojis et autocollants.
description_localizations.hi: सर्वर को न्यूनतम स्थिति में रीसेट करता है: चैनल, रोल (@everyone को छोड़कर), इमोजी और स्टिकर हटाता है।
description_localizations.hr: Vraća poslužitelj na minimalno stanje: uklanja kanale, uloge (osim @everyone), emojije i naljepnice.
description_localizations.hu: A szervert minimális állapotra állítja vissza: eltávolítja a csatornákat, szerepeket (@everyone kivételével), emojikat és matricákat.
description_localizations.id: Mengatur ulang server ke kondisi minimum: menghapus saluran, peran (kecuali @everyone), emoji, dan stiker.
description_localizations.it: Ripristina il server allo stato minimo: rimuove canali, ruoli (tranne @everyone), emoji e adesivi.
description_localizations.ja: サーバーを最小構成にリセットします：チャンネル、ロール（@everyone 以外）、絵文字、ステッカーを削除します。
description_localizations.ko: 서버를 최소 상태로 초기화합니다: 채널, 역할(@everyone 제외), 이모지 및 스티커를 제거합니다.
description_localizations.lt: Atstato serverį į minimalų lygį: pašalina kanalus, roles (išskyrus @everyone), jaustukus ir lipdukus.
description_localizations.nl: Zet de server terug naar de minimale staat: verwijdert kanalen, rollen (behalve @everyone), emoji’s en stickers.
description_localizations.no: Tilbakestiller serveren til minimum: fjerner kanaler, roller (unntatt @everyone), emojier og klistremerker.
description_localizations.pl: Przywraca serwer do minimalnego stanu: usuwa kanały, role (oprócz @everyone), emoji i naklejki.
description_localizations.pt-BR: Redefine o servidor para o estado mínimo: remove canais, cargos (exceto @everyone), emojis e figurinhas.
description_localizations.ro: Resetează serverul la starea minimă: elimină canale, roluri (cu excepția @everyone), emoji și stickere.
description_localizations.ru: Сбрасывает сервер к минимальному состоянию: удаляет каналы, роли (кроме @everyone), эмодзи и стикеры.
description_localizations.sv-SE: Återställer servern till minimalt läge: tar bort kanaler, roller (förutom @everyone), emojis och klistermärken.
description_localizations.th: รีเซ็ตเซิร์ฟเวอร์เป็นค่าเริ่มต้นขั้นต่ำ: ลบช่อง, ยศ (@everyone ยังคงอยู่), อีโมจิ และสติกเกอร์
description_localizations.tr: Sunucuyu minimum duruma sıfırlar: kanalları, rolleri (@everyone hariç), emojileri ve çıkartmaları kaldırır.
description_localizations.uk: Скидає сервер до мінімального стану: видаляє канали, ролі (крім @everyone), емодзі та стікери.
description_localizations.vi: Đặt lại máy chủ về trạng thái tối thiểu: xóa kênh, vai trò (trừ @everyone), emoji và nhãn dán.
description_localizations.zh-CN: 将服务器重置为最小默认状态：删除频道、身份组（保留 @everyone）、表情和贴纸。
description_localizations.zh-TW: 將伺服器重設為最小預設狀態：移除頻道、身分組（保留 @everyone）、表情符號與貼紙。

description_localizations.es-ES: Si es verdadero, solo simula (predeterminado: true)

description_localizations.hr: Ako je true, samo simulira (zadano: true)
